8658	\begin{proof}
8659	  \uses{lem:map_augment_cond}
8660	  The two augmented complexes have, by construction, the same underlying graded object:
8661	  in degree \(0\) both read \(\Phi Y\), and in degree \(n+1\) both read \(\Phi C^n\). Define
